Place a wallpaper image named `wallpaper.png` in this directory to use it as the
default wallpaper for all themes that do not ship their own image.

nixpalette will pick it up automatically at build time — no configuration needed.

To override it per-user, set:

  nixpalette.defaultWallpaper = ./path/to/your/wallpaper.png;

Supported formats: PNG (recommended), JPEG, any format supported by ImageMagick.
Any resolution works; Stylix and your compositor handle scaling.
